select
max(name) as name,
max(r_t_tanggal) as r_t_tanggal,
r_t_member_id,
sum(r_t_detail_nominal + r_t_detail_nominal_pajak + r_t_detail_nominal_sc) as nilaibeli
from "users" left join "rekap_transaksi" on CAST(r_t_member_id AS bigint) = "users_id" inner join "rekap_transaksi_detail" on "r_t_detail_r_t_id" = "r_t_id" inner join "m_w" on "m_w_id" = "waroeng_id" inner join "m_area" on "m_area_id" = "m_w_m_area_id" left join "m_produk" on "m_produk_id" = "r_t_detail_m_produk_id" where LENGTH(r_t_member_id) = 5 and "m_produk_m_jenis_produk_id" = '11' and "m_w_m_area_id" = '5' and "waroeng_id" = '58' and "r_t_tanggal" = '2023-11-07' group by "r_t_member_id" order by "nilaibeli" desc
